  "text": "While the kinase function of IKKα is dispensable for keratinocyte differentiation, stratifin is downregulated in IKKα-deficient keratinocytes, reintroduction of IKKα restoring the SFN expression [CITATION_1] . Although a biochemical interaction between IRF6 and stratifin/IKKα has not been demonstrated, Irf6 and Sfn interact epistatically to control periderm development [CITATION_2] .",
